            <div class="vendor-tag">Travel / cab vendor</div>
            <div class="vendor-title">I manage travel or cab services</div>
            <p class="vendor-desc">
              For cab operators, bus companies and travel agencies.
            </p>
          </div>

          <ul>
            <li>Add routes, timings and seat details</li>
            <li>Manage bookings across all services</li>
            <li>Increase visibility to thousands of users</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="/vendor/travel/login" class="btn btn-primary vendor-btn">
